description: This file defines Pydantic models for API request schemas related to team sessions, team runs, and team creation within a backend system.

classes.name: TeamSessionCreate
classes.description: Schema for creating a team session, includes session ID and optional team data.

classes.name: TeamRunCreate
classes.description: Schema for creating a team run, includes session ID, optional team session ID, run ID, run data, and team data.

classes.name: TeamCreate
classes.description: Schema for creating a team, includes team ID, optional parent team ID, app ID, workflow ID, name, and configuration.
